<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Maruti Coaching Classes</title>

<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">

<style>
*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:Arial,sans-serif;
}

body{
background:#f5f7fb;
color:#222;
}

header{
position:fixed;
width:100%;
top:0;
left:0;
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;
padding:15px 8%;
background:rgba(0,0,50,.8);
backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
z-index:1000;
}

.logo{
color:#fff;
font-size:28px;
font-weight:bold;
}

nav a{
color:#fff;
text-decoration:none;
margin-left:20px;
transition:.3s;
}

nav a:hover{
color:gold;
}

.hero{
height:100vh;
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
text-align:center;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f2027,#203a43,#2c5364);
color:white;
padding:20px;
}

.hero h1{
font-size:55px;
margin-bottom:15px;
animation:fadeDown 1s;
}

.hero p{
font-size:22px;
margin-bottom:30px;
animation:fadeUp 1.5s;
}

.btn{
display:inline-block;
padding:15px 35px;
background:gold;
color:black;
border-radius:30px;
text-decoration:none;
font-weight:bold;
transition:.3s;
}

.btn:hover{
transform:scale(1.08);
}

@keyframes fadeDown{
from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(-60px);}
to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}
}

@keyframes fadeUp{
from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(60px);}
to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}
}
</style>

</head>

<body>

<header>
<div class="logo">Maruti Coaching</div>

<nav>
<a href="#">Home</a>
<a href="#">About</a>
<a href="#">Courses</a>
<a href="#">Gallery</a>
<a href="#">Contact</a>
</nav>

</header>

<section class="hero">

<div>

<h1>Maruti Coaching Classes</h1>

<p>Admission Open 2026-27 <br>
Nursery to Class 10 (MP Board)<br><br>

📍 Sarkari School ke Piche, Vikramgarh, Alot<br>

🕔 Evening Batch : 5:00 PM - 8:00 PM

</p>

<a href="https://wa.me/916267311721" class="btn">
Apply on WhatsApp
</a>

</div>

</section>

</body>
</html>